Package gwtupload.client

Interface Summary
HasJsData Interface for Classes having a method returning a javascript object with information about the instance.
HasProgress Interface for Classes having a method to update progress
IFileInput Interface used by Uploaders to use and configure a customized file input.
IFileInput.HasFileInputType interface for FileInputType enum
IsUpdateable Interface for objects that can be notified periodically to update their status.
IUploader Interface that represents uploader panels.
IUploader.OnCancelUploaderHandler Interface for onCancelUpload events.
IUploader.OnChangeUploaderHandler Interface for onChangeUpload events.
IUploader.OnFinishUploaderHandler Interface for onFinishUpload events.
IUploader.OnStartUploaderHandler Interface for onStartUpload events.
IUploader.OnStatusChangedHandler Interface for onStatusChanged events.
IUploader.UploaderConstants Interface for localizable elements.
IUploadStatus Interface used by uploaders to notify the progress status.
IUploadStatus.UploadCancelHandler Handler called when the user clicks on the cancel button.
IUploadStatus.UploadStatusChangedHandler Handler called when the status changes.
IUploadStatus.UploadStatusConstants Interface for internationalizable elements.
PreloadedImage.OnErrorPreloadedImageHandler Handler called when the image load raises an error.
PreloadedImage.OnLoadPreloadedImageHandler Handler called when the image is loaded successfully.
 

Class Summary
BaseUploadStatus Basic widget that implements the IUploadStatus interface.
DecoratedFileUpload A decorated file upload is a widget which hides a FileUpload showing a clickable and customizable Widget, normally a button.
DecoratedFileUpload.FileUploadWithMouseEvents A FileUpload which implements onChange, onMouseOver and onMouseOut events.
IFileInput.AnchorFileInput A HyperLinkFileInput implementing the IFileInput interface
IFileInput.BrowserFileInput Just a FileUpload which implements the interface IFileInput
IFileInput.ButtonFileInput A DecoratedFileInput implementing the IFileInput interface
IFileInput.LabelFileInput A LabelFileInput implementing the IFileInput interface
IUploader.Utils Utility class.
ModalUploadStatus Modal progress widget that implements the IUploadStatus interface.
MultiUploader Implementation of an uploader panel that is able to handle several uploads.
PreloadedImage  
SingleUploader Implementation of a single uploader panel with a submit button.
UpdateTimer A timer that notifies periodically to IUpdateable classes.
Uploader Uploader panel.
 

Enum Summary
IFileInput.FileInputType Enum for different IFileInput implementations
IUploadStatus.CancelBehavior Enumeration of possible cancel options
IUploadStatus.Status Enumeration of possible status values
